public final class ThreadedApssTask<S>
extends NaiveApssTask<S>

An all pairs similarity search implementation that parallelises another implementation. This is achieved by breaking the work down into chunks that are run concurrently.

Author:
Hamish I A Morgan <hamish.morgan@sussex.ac.uk>
